snippet.title: SpongeBob SquarePants: Clash Of Triton - PC Gameplay HD
snippet.description:
SpongeBob SquarePants: Clash Of Triton - PC Gameplay HD

Subscribe here ►►► http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=FirstPlaysHD
Also SHARE, COMMENT, LIKE ☺

Join SpongeBob and Patrick as they fight to break Triton's spell over Bikini Bottom! Unleash the power of the gods to demolish Triton's warped cities, fight off armies of Krabby Patty soldiers, and restore Bikini Bottom to its former glory. Play as different versions of SpongeBob and Patrick, and earn smiting points to power them up with unique abilities until they are virtually unstoppable!


░▒▓ PC Hardware ▓▒░

CPU: Intel Core i7 3770K @ 4.20 Ghz
RAM: 8 GB
GPU: ASUS GTX760-DC2OC-2GD5
OS:  Windows 7 64bit


░▒▓ Recording HW ▓▒░

Avermedia live Gamer HD
